---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Our Roadmap | Mellon"
  description="Mellon's roadmap: joining the Chronocat ecosystem for ADHD productivity, AI companions, and Mellon AI for B2B automation."
>
  <section class="roadmap-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="roadmap-title">Our Roadmap</h1>
      <p class="roadmap-intro">
        Mellon is part of a broader vision for productivity and AI. Here's where we're headed.
      </p>

      <div class="roadmap-content">
        <div class="roadmap-card">
          <h2>Chronocat Ecosystem</h2>
          <p>
            We're adding Mellon to our ecosystem of <a href="https://chronocat.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener">chronocat.app</a>—a productivity app designed for ADHD. Chronocat helps you stay focused and organized, and Mellon brings voice-first input to that experience.
          </p>
          <p>
            Together, we're building an <strong>AI companion</strong> and <strong>personal assistant</strong> that will interact with your calendar, act as an ADHD coach, and help you achieve your goals. Think of it as a coach for personal productivity—always there to help you stay on track.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="roadmap-card">
          <h2>Mellon Projects</h2>
          <p>
            Mellon also joins our ecosystem of <strong>Mellon Projects</strong>. At the heart of this is <strong>Mellon AI</strong>—a B2B service for small to medium-sized businesses.
          </p>
          <p>
            Mellon AI helps businesses set up AI automation, AI assistants, AI employees, AI SEO specialists, and AI marketing specialists. We bring enterprise-grade AI capabilities to teams that want to move fast without the complexity.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="roadmap-summary">
          <p>
            <strong>In short:</strong> Mellon Voice is the consumer-facing voice dictation tool. Chronocat is the ADHD productivity app. Mellon AI is the B2B arm for business automation. Together, they form a cohesive ecosystem for getting more done—whether you're an individual or a business.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .roadmap-section {
    padding: var(--space-5xl) 0;
    min-height: 60vh;
  }

  .roadmap-title {
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .roadmap-intro {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-4xl);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .roadmap-content {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .roadmap-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    transition: border-color var(--transition-normal);
  }

  .roadmap-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
  }

  .roadmap-card h2 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .roadmap-card p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .roadmap-card p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .roadmap-card a {
    color: var(--color-accent-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .roadmap-card a:hover {
    border-bottom-color: var(--color-accent-primary);
  }

  .roadmap-summary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.08) 0%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.05) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .roadmap-summary p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .roadmap-section {
      padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
    }

    .roadmap-card {
      padding: var(--space-xl);
    }
  }
</style>
